reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 5, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Useful for Overpackers
reviews.reviewText: These were exactly what I wanted. They allowed me to take a smaller suitcase and I still had room for some souvenirs. They’re cute and the different sizes are wonderful, and they pack very nicely. The straps in the larger bags are great for organizing. I folded my 2 fancier items and a light jacket and strapped them in the bottom of the medium cube, and put my regular clothes on top. I didn’t have to dig for anything and it was really easy to find what I needed for the day. The shoe bag is great and it expands. I’m a size 8 US women’s shoe, and I could fit a pair of tennis shoes, a pair of converse, and 2 sandals into the bag. Honestly, the only things really missing from this set is sizable laundry bag (though I used the larger zippered bag for my dirty shirts and intimates and it was totally workable) and the quality of the fabric was a little cheap. My largest cube came with a small tear in the side of the mesh, but it didn’t affect the function at all and it was super easy for me to repair with a sewing kit. Overall, highly useful items and it came in my favorite color, so I’m more than pleased with what I got for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 29, 2022
reviews.reviewText: These cubes made our packing lives so much easier! I was able to coordinate my girls’ clothing by color of these cubes, and all their outfits for an 8 day road trip (granted we washed clothes during the trip), were able to fit neatly in these cubes. The cubes then fit in a regular sized backpack for each girl. There was room to spare in the backpacks, which left plenty of room for 2 cubes per kid, their snacks, games, and other activities! Great purchase! These are kind of flimsy, so I’m not sure how long they’ll last, but the price wasn’t bad.
